Glasgow native Stuart, 55, whom I follow from Sister Ray (count: two young women, three middle-aged men) to Reckless Records (count: eight middle-aged men, one woman, probably in his twenties), spends his afternoon in London for a meeting, and wanders the shops to spend a few hours.
