Video: The Heila puppy is Tulli&#39;s newest dog reinforcement - the puppy will become the first explosive dog
A black labrador retriever puppy energetically sniffs five similar boxes lined up on the ground at Helsinki-Vantaa airport.
It won&#39;t be long before it sits resolutely next to the middle drawer.
Customs inspector Lassi Suntio rewards his dog Heila for playing with its favorite toy.
